snippet.title: Johnny Depp, Amber Heard Settle Divorce Case
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Agree to Settle Divorce Case | The former couple released a joint statement.

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard filed documents on Tuesday to end their divorce case. Heard has withdrawn her domestic abuse restraining order against Depp .

The actor has reportedly agreed to pay his ex $7 million and she's dropped her domestic violence restraining order. Subscribe: About E!

After a public feud complete with charges of abuse and manipulation, irreconcilable differences led Amber Heard to file for divorce against husband Johnny .
